	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Most of them display that in the "hidden" top 8 rows I guess. We have yet to find a game that actually relies on that feature to display proper graphics on the palyfield. I guess by having all 4 BG palettes identical you could use that feature to extend the playfield to become 32x32 instead of 32x30.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


